	 ('Brainwave Cafe','94/732 Harris St, Ultimo, Sydney, New South Wales','+61-404016006','Closed temporarily','Cuisine: Vegan, Thai, Fast food, Asian, Fusion, Australian, Breakfast','Crafting food with Asian influences juxtaposed with modern Australian. Features dishes like burgers like ''pulled pork'' and ''fissh burgers'' all topped with relish and sauces; stir fries and salads; additional options like deep-fried mushrooms and tofu salads served with vegan dressing; mango chia pudding and creme brulee with coconut sorbet for dessert. Beverages are coffee, cold brew coffee, cold press juices, and organic teas. Fully vegan since August 2020.'),
	 ('Bodhi in the Park','4 College St, Sydney, New South Wales','+61-293602523','Mon-Sat 11:00am-3:00pm, Tue-Sat 5:00pm-10:00pm, Sun 11:00am-4:00pm','Cuisine: Vegan, Chinese, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Asian','Finer dining set amongst Hyde Park by St Mary''s Cathedral. Serves yum cha at lunch with dishes coming out regularly from the kitchen during peak time. Asian style meals at dinner. No garlic or onion used. Fully vegan, including alcohol, since Jun 2019. Instagram @bodhirestaurantbar.'),
	 ('Bodhi Restaurant Bar','2-4 College St, Sydney, New South Wales','+61-293602523','Tue-Sat 11:00am-3:00pm, Tue-Sun 5:00pm-10:00pm, Sun 11:00am-4:00pm','Cuisine: Vegan, Asian','An all-vegan Asian restaurant/bar located in the middle of the City.'),
	 ('Iku Wholefoods Kitchen - Martin Place','MLC Centre Food Court, Martin Place (at Pitt St), Sydney, New South Wales','+61-292338001','Mon-Fri 8:30am-4:00pm','Cuisine: Vegan, Macrobiotic, Fast food, Take-out','Ready made meals for dine-in or takeaway.'),
	 ('Joe''s Sandwich Bar','292 Kent St, Sydney CBD, Sydney, New South Wales','Add a phone number','Mon-Fri 11:30am-3:00pm','Cuisine: Vegan, Western, Fast food, Take-out','Vegan sandwich bar opened 2017. Serves coffee, treats, and sandwiches with different fillings such as tempeh reuben, miso eggplant, mock salmon, and greens. No telephone - contact via social media. Instagram @joessandwichbar.'),
	 ('Sanga','5/655 King St, St Peters, Sydney, New South Wales','+61-416844700','Thu 7:30am-8:30pm, Fri 11:30am-9:30pm, Sat 10:00am-9:30pm','Cuisine: Vegan, American, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery','Vegan subway style bar. A project of Bhavani Baumann who co-founded Australia\\u2019s first vegan pub bistro - The Green Lion, in 2016. Offers freshly baked hot rolls with fillings and sauces to build own. Has a pie range, gluten free rolls and salad bowls on the menu too. Sweets include a range of house-made soft style cookies, cheesecake cups and lamingtons. Also has a range of beers, wines and cocktails. Open since Nov ''21.'),
	 ('Voodie Burger ','Broadway Shopping Centre, Sydney, New South Wales','Add a phone number','Now Open:                     Mon-Wed 5:00pm-9:00pm, Thu-Sat 5:00pm-10:00pm, Sun 5:00pm-9:00pm','Cuisine: Vegan, American, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Fusion, Australian','Kiosk 230 inside Broadway Shopping Centre serving fully vegan burgers in fusion flavors. Est. 2020. May get delivery via ubereats.'),
	 ('Alibi','6 Cowper Wharf Roadway, Woolloomooloo, Sydney, New South Wales','+61-293319088','Now Open:                     Mon-Wed 4:00pm-9:00pm, Thu-Fri 6:00pm-12:00am, Sat 12:00pm-12:00am, Sun 3:00pm-11:30pm','Cuisine: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Raw, Western, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Fusion, Australian','A Matthew Kenney restaurant & bar, est. 2018 inside Ovolo Hotel. Offers gourmet plant-based cuisine that''s mostly vegan except for dairy cheese and milk options and non-vegan alcohol. Instagram @alibisydney. Confirmed open May 2020.'),
	 ('Flyover Fritterie & Chai Bar','1 Temperance Lane, Sydney, New South Wales','+61-415908085','Mon-Fri 11:00am-3:00pm','Cuisine: Lacto, Indian, Fast food, Take-out, Fusion, Gluten-free','Fritterie and chai bar est. 2019 in the laneway next to 389 George St, near the train stations Wynyard and Town Hall. Serves chickpea flour & vegetable pakoras (fritters), street style salads, quinoa khichri, pao burgers, and Indian chai (tea). Order at the window, and have your meal at one of the benches in the laneway. No longer fully vegan as of Oct 2021.'),
	 ('Health Nuts Shop & Cafe','Shop TG04 82-94 Darlinghurst Rd, Kings Cross Centre, Potts Point, Sydney, New South Wales','+61-293315370','Now Open:                     Mon-Thu 7:00am-9:00pm, Fri 7:00am-8:00pm, Sat 8:00am-9:00pm, Sun 8:00am-6:00pm','Cuisine: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Organic, Raw, Western, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, Gluten-free, Australian','Organic cafe within the health food store where most of the dishes are vegan and gluten-free. Offers prepared salads bar and dishes like vegan cheeseburger, carrot dog, pulled \\u2018vork\\u2019 sliders, vegan egg, and quiche. Has cabinet selection of vegan cakes and raw desserts. Fresh juices, protein smoothies, and espresso drinks available.');
