	 ('Peace Harmony','29 King St, Sydney, New South Wales','+61-292990419','Mon-Thu 11:00am-3:00pm','Cuisine: Vegan-friendly, Thai, Take-out','Small cafe serving veggie Thai food. Everything is vegan except for vitamilk (Thai) soy milk drink. Confirmed open December 2021.'),
	 ('Yellow','57 Macleay St, Sydney, New South Wales','+61-293322344','Now Open:                     Mon-Fri 6:00pm-10:00pm, Sat-Sun 11:00am-10:00pm','Cuisine: Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Take-out, European, French, Australian','Upscale vegetarian dining restaurant and bar. A la carte and tasting menus. Focus is on heirloom varietals grown by local suppliers. Note: Vegan options may be quite limited. Confirmed open May 2020.'),
